# Layout (`shared/shell` + `shared/ui`)

## App shell (`shared/shell/`)

Single layout for guest + user + admin portals — **no sidebar**, **no footer**.

- `AppShellComponent` (`app-shell`) — `app-topbar` + scrollable `.app-shell__content` + `<router-outlet>` (no portal accent host class)
- Content padding: `styles/_shell-content.scss` mixin; breakpoint via `styles/_breakpoints.scss`

Registered in `app.routes.ts` as parent of all routes (guest pages + lazy portal trees).

## App topbar (`shared/shell/app-topbar/`)

Modes from `AuthService` + optional `PORTAL_CONFIG`:

| Mode | Left zone | Right zone |
|------|-----------|------------|
| **guest** | Brand; Register always; Sign in link when not on `/` | theme → language |
| **user** | Brand + **create** `+` menu (left) | theme → language → notifications → account |
| **admin** | Brand → `homeUrl` + **create** `+` menu | theme → language → account |

- `ThemePickerComponent` / `LanguagePickerComponent` — `shared/ui/`; single-click toggles
- `BrandMarkComponent` — admin topbar shows neutral **ADMIN** suffix (`--text-muted`) via `PortalConfig.shell.brandSuffixKey`; user topbar shows plain BHCOM
- **`EntityCreateMenuComponent`** (`shared/shell/app-topbar/entity-create-menu/`) — shared `+` dropdown for user and admin; per-option `entityTab` for colored spine + icon; options from `USER_OFFER_OPTIONS` / `ADMIN_CREATE_OPTIONS`; aria: `shared.topbar.offer.openMenu` (user) / `shared.topbar.create.openMenu` (admin)
- Account menu: **My listings** / **Moje objave** (`LucideListChecks`, user → `userOurListingsUrl()`), settings (admin → `ADMIN_SETTINGS_URL`), logout → `SIGN_IN_URL`
- Styles: `styles/_topbar.scss` (`topbar-base`, `topbar-icon-btn`)

## Portal config & topbar nav

- `PORTAL_CONFIG` provided on lazy portal branches in `app.routes.ts` (`USER_PORTAL_CONFIG`, `ADMIN_PORTAL_CONFIG`)
- `PortalConfig.topbarNav: TopbarNavItem[]` — `{ labelKey, route, exact? }`
- User: `portal/user/user-topbar-nav.config.ts` — empty (`topbarNav: []`); browse via brand → `USER_HOME_URL`; create via hub tab CTA + `EntityCreateMenuComponent`
- Admin: `topbarNav: []` — hub tabs in-page at `/admin/home`; tab-specific create CTA in hub page header + `EntityCreateMenuComponent` in topbar

## Shared UI widgets (`shared/ui/`)

- `PageTitleComponent` — portal `h1` + subtitle + icon; hubs use `.page-hub-header` — see `page-title.mdc`
- `PageBackLinkComponent` — above title on portal create/edit forms — see `page-title.mdc`
- `RouteDisplayComponent`, `VehicleDisplayComponent`, `DateRangeDisplayComponent`, `WarehouseDisplayComponent`, `StatusBadgeComponent` — table cells; see `tables.mdc`
- `DatePeriodPickerComponent` — filter + form date input — see `forms.mdc`, `table-filters.mdc`
- `PageHeaderComponent` + `PrimaryActionLinkComponent` — list page + hub tab create CTA — see `page-title.mdc`
- `EntityTabsComponent` — hub tab bar; user + admin hubs use default `accentMode="entity"` — see `entity-tabs.mdc`
- **Hub header:** `.page-hub-header` (`styles/_page-hub-header.scss`) — user marketplace (Tržište) / my listings (Moje objave) / admin home — see `entity-tabs.mdc`

## Styling

- Use `@use 'styles/breakpoints' as *` + `@include below-md` in layout SCSS
- **Mobile breakpoint:** `shared/constants/viewport.ts` — `MOBILE_MEDIA_QUERY` (`max-width: 768px`); used by `DataTableComponent`, `FormStepperComponent`
- **Theme surfaces:** 4-layer stack — see `theme-tokens.mdc`. Topbar = chrome; page canvas = `--bg-app`
- **Portal accent (guest only):** user green / admin blue on picker cards + login/register pages (`login--user`, `login--admin`, `register--admin`, `portal-card--*`); tokens in `src/styles/_portal-accent.scss`. Authenticated shell/topbar use neutral chrome — **no** `--portal-accent` on portal page content.

